<text top="855" left="97" width="720" height="12" font="3">________________________________________________________________________________</text>
<text top="890" left="142" width="675" height="12" font="3">This record contains the original text of speeches delivered in English and</text>
<text top="908" left="97" width="459" height="12" font="3">interpretations of speeches in the other languages.</text>
<text top="908" left="574" width="198" height="12" font="3">The final text will be</text>
<text top="926" left="97" width="504" height="12" font="3">printed in the Official Records of the Security Council.</text>
<text top="961" left="142" width="522" height="12" font="3">Corrections should be submitted to original speeches only.</text>
<text top="961" left="682" width="126" height="12" font="3">They should be</text>
